there is

18
00:01:02,390 --> 00:01:03,600
no way

19
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:05,430
to get rid of the root of her illness.

20
00:01:06,390 --> 00:01:07,890
I can only write you a prescription

21
00:01:08,430 --> 00:01:10,260
